title: Girl - Yes We CANada
description: Girl Skateboards' Koston, McCrank, Jereme Rogers and the new kids, Malto and Mike Mo, tour Eastern Canada. Local legend Dan Bochart guides their way. This is Mike Mo and Malto's first trip with the Girl team, also the first time they met each other. Both were very confused when Koston showed up at the airport with golf clubs. The tour video is followed by “welcome” parts of Sean and Mo.
